  "active_lock_reason": "resolved",
  "body": "Calling the `getContractAt` helper currently fails if the contract needs library linking.\r\n\r\n```js\r\nconst token = await ethers.getContractAt(\"Token\", address);\r\n```\r\n\r\nThis can be worked around like this for now:\r\n```js\r\nconst tokenArtifact = await artifacts.readArtifact(\"Token\");\r\nconst token = new ethers.Contract(address, tokenArtifact.abi, ethers.provider);\r\n```",
